<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
div{
  width:300px;
  height:100px;
  background-color:pink;
  border: 1px solid black;
}

.rotate:hover{
  -ms-transform:rotate(20deg);
  -webkit-transform:rotate(20deg);
  transform:rotate(-20deg);
}
.translate:hover{
  -ms-transform:translate(50px,100px);
  -webkit-transform:translate(50px,100px);
  transform:translate(50px,100px);
}
.scalediv:hover{
  -ms-transform:scale(2,3);
  -webkit-transform:scale(2,3);
  transform:scaleY(2);
}
.skewdiv:hover{
-ms-transform:skewX(20deg);
-webkit-transform:skewX(20deg);
transform:skew(20deg,10deg);
}

.matrixdiv:hover{
  -ms-transform:matrix(1,-0.3,0,1,0,0);
  -webkit-transform:matrix(1,-0.3,0,1,0,0);
  transform:matrix(1,-0.3,0,1,2,8);
}



      </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>The rotate effect</h1>
    <p>rotate can rotate clockwise or anticlockwise</p>
    <div class="rotate">
      Am I rotating?
    </div>
    <h1>The translate effect</h1>
    <div class="translate">
      Catch me!
    </div>
    <h1>The scale effect</h1>
    <div class="scalediv">
      Am I getting bigger or smaller?
    </div>
    <h1>The Skew Effect</h1>
    <div class="skewdiv">
      I am skewed !
    </div>
    <h1>The matrix Effect</h1>
    <div class="matrixdiv">
      I am doing all the 2D moves
    </div>
  </body>

